@LecturaIA.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5267

### ============================================
### TEST CUESTIONARIOS CON OPENAI
### ============================================

### PASO 1: Login como Estudiante
# @name login
POST {{LecturaIA.API_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "mf2018000597@virtual.upt.pe",
  "password": "Almosteasy123@"
}

###

### PASO 2: Generar cuestionario para sesión existente
POST {{LecturaIA.API_HostAddress}}/api/Cuestionarios/generar
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "sesionLecturaId": "27CE0ACF-D019-4370-B723-0F2C9365CF2"
}

###

### PASO 3: Obtener lecturas disponibles
GET {{LecturaIA.API_HostAddress}}/api/Lecturas
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###

### PASO 4: Ver estado del cuestionario
GET {{LecturaIA.API_HostAddress}}/api/Cuestionarios/sesion/27CE0ACF-D019-4370-B723-0F2C9365CF2
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

###
